{"tid":328497,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"新加坡另類遊","createTime":"2017-07-19T15:23:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-24T10:51:09.000Z","uid":54593,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7c63e674f77a99cc2b59853554e0fff7be5e492f","tid":328497,"uid":54593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T15:23:59.000Z","msg":"話說上個月獨遊去左東南亞幾個國家旅行，其中一站係新加坡。<br />\n今次決定分享下係新加坡3日既所見所聞同感受。<br />\n另外因為小弟獨遊所以去既地方比較另類同悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，冇去到聖淘沙動物園呢D大路景點。<br />\n希望呢篇短短既遊記可以令各位巴絲認識新加坡另外既一面，同埋避免旅遊伏位！<br />\nps. 第一次去新加坡<br />\n<br />\n行程簡介<br />\n第1日  被誦經聲嘈醒<br />\n<em>Arab Street &rarr; 市中心 &rarr; Marina Bay &rarr; Gardens by the Bay</em><br />\n第2日  神怪鬼秘的主題公園<br />\n<em>虎豹別墅 &rarr; 南部山脊 &rarr; 牛車水</em><br />\n第3日  星洲獨有的霸位文化(?)<br />\n<em>Vivo City &rarr; 麥里芝蓄水池 &rarr; TreeTop Walk</em><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/6iey7p90\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F6iey7p90&h=86dc5608&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第1日 <br />\nArab Street<br />\n旅社位於Arab Street 區域，晨早流流就被街外清真寺誦經既聲音嘈醒。食完早餐去附近周圍行下睇下發生乜事，好多穆斯林着哂傳統服飾從蘇丹回教堂出黎。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/19/231943_93e40408172c843b1d3b6f2ef15688f3.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F19%2F231943_93e40408172c843b1d3b6f2ef15688f3.JPG&h=010ed807&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一班又一班人係附近聚集留影吹水，勁熱鬧。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/h4e5mlr0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fh4e5mlr0&h=425e6731&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n原來呢一日係伊斯蘭教既開齋節(Hari Raya Puasa)，係慶祝齋月結束既大日子，亦都係新加坡既法定假期。<br />\n連地鐵都有為節日裝飾下車箱<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/kcry923q\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fkcry923q&h=91c28e99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n晏晝落過一場雷雨，停雨之後係市中心漫遊。<br />\n睇下魚尾獅 個樣好楚楚可憐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/csuw0fkt\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fcsuw0fkt&h=407eeac5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n假日既新加坡街頭，好有香港既感覺 -- 人多擠迫<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/rhkgx1sl\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Frhkgx1sl&h=4ba3837b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n馬來印印城市野餐<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/8dxqib9m\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F8dxqib9m&h=abadae28&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在濱海灣徒步走到去Gardens by the Bay，一直都想去睇睇既大花園。<br />\nSupertree 真係幾靚，外型似外星人基地，好有未來感。<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/banejxhd\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fbanejxhd&h=1b607677&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n心裡極期待七點幾既Supertree light show，可惜期望愈大失望愈大，原來以為supertree樹冠會着燈五顏六色隨音樂閃爍，點知只係得射燈射黎射去，完全無驚喜。伏！<img src=\"https://holland.pk/wrf1zyud\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fwrf1zyud&h=561e6769&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n千其唔好哂時間睇，慳返D時間去對面金沙賭幾鋪好過。"},{"pid":"462a15cd889c7597f4e9098a93117897805b483d","tid":328497,"uid":54593,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T15:32:29.000Z","msg":"第2日<br />\n今日天氣超好，藍天白雲有陽光。<br />\n朝早去左虎豹別墅，中式既舊主題公園。香港個個一早摺左，唯有新加坡呢度保存良好。入口既裝飾已經好詭異，用肥牛黎做背景。<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/i32pru67\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fi32pru67&h=93a93afa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n園內有好多殘殘地既公仔雕塑，有D係描繪中國民間傳說既故事，例如八仙、西遊記等等，有D就唔知代表乜野奇奇怪怪咁。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/7vw1ufrp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F7vw1ufrp&h=5b9554b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n當中最恐怖既係 地獄十殿Ten Courts of Hell，入去參觀地獄既苦況。<br />\n生前做過壞事就會被鬼卒帶去照鏡，照下自己作惡既衰樣。<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/6zv5r9mf\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F6zv5r9mf&h=bcabfdfa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n根據唔同既罪行會有唔同既懲罰，老實講雕塑做得幾迫真，細路仔睇完應該以後唔敢做壞事。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後第十殿就係講輪迴轉世，壞人飲完孟婆湯洗去前世既記憶，就會輪迴去三惡道。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/19/233111_b08072410005fd836864c664d0845531.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F19%2F233111_b08072410005fd836864c664d0845531.JPG&h=2794bdcd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n係虎豹別墅大概行左一個鍾都睇哂所有野。<br />\n下晝去food court食叻沙補充體力，然後向南部山脊出發。新加坡平地多山丘少，而且最高既山只有一百幾十米，但係綠化比率都好高，唔會將所有土地拎哂去起樓。<br />\n<br />\n起點係新加坡科學園，好奇怪一個人都冇，後來先知道今日係開齋節補假。<img src=\"https://holland.pk/jmehu81o\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fjmehu81o&h=de033040&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n望住Google Map搵路，搵到目標小路進入肯特崗公園<br />\n新加坡郊野似乎比較多呢種高空步道，在熱帶叢林既樹上行走，令遊人可以享受無樹遮掩既開揚景觀。<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/ruo1829w\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fruo1829w&h=0092b5cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/clz0a41d\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fclz0a41d&h=8c64ff8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n由肯特崗公園一路向東行，走到亨德森波浪橋。波浪橋係新加坡離地最高既行人橋，造型呈波浪形態，天橋步道用木板搭建，設計特別。<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/5s1dyqzr\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F5s1dyqzr&h=16947a06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後再繼續行去花柏山，腳開始攰。<br />\n全程烈日當空行左7公里，落左山對面就係VivoCity，可以休息下。<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/dj25ney0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fdj25ney0&h=989d15f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n四五點坐地鐵去牛車水，係華人既地盤。<br />\n係牛車水美食街食左碟好撚難食既炒粿條<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n睇大媽舞係旅程中既Must do item<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/19/233134_ed730bba69ed94c59547f1b2624d69c2.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F19%2F233134_ed730bba69ed94c59547f1b2624d69c2.JPG&h=f0f8c0fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n待續"},{"pid":"4d379267bcb1bd1c5bfa27a061f60fa2d34f54c4","tid":328497,"uid":69049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T17:13:50.000Z","msg":"留名想獨遊新加坡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0148e92aedef93a4f59550d3f4e1364f2a03917","tid":328497,"uid":10804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T17:19:33.000Z","msg":"下次去虎豹別墅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abd9ac6e3e61dbabf116055b8ad946a960fd321f","tid":328497,"uid":1694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T18:00:53.000Z","msg":"九月去新加坡"},{"pid":"0cc7f2b0d159447328dc98abae46a380dc1f614a","tid":328497,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T18:03:38.000Z","msg":"流明"},{"pid":"5110a2320f70ab066e33848969f98c1e8f363469","tid":328497,"uid":38376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T19:20:27.000Z","msg":"幾好喎個公園"},{"pid":"b87d04764a3fb961eb7c8faf4650ebac9d85588c","tid":328497,"uid":47041,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T22:56:40.000Z","msg":"新加坡真係去過一次可以以後都唔洗去"},{"pid":"4ddf2f529d853c101f83ebd69293febb88e072e4","tid":328497,"uid":61462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T23:25:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b755d96a8318146c6f8945ced85b191412d7b256","tid":328497,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T01:52:00.000Z","msg":"睇來新加玻麻麻地好玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a81a8a93f9b2cd978b48e1c1dc6e9d22d6beba8","tid":328497,"uid":54593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T04:23:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>新加坡真係去過一次可以以後都唔洗去</blockquote><br />\n真。<br />\n第一次去都係貪新鮮，但留係星加坡多過兩日 呢種新鮮感好快消失。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbfc9f974e31fb8f9ed68493beef083753df5b39","tid":328497,"uid":54593,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T04:26:14.000Z","msg":"第3日<br />\n「新加坡很無聊，就一個小島有什麼好玩的。」<br />\n呢日成日都陰天落住雨，去左vivo city行下商場。<br />\n最後呢篇主要係想分享下係新加坡遇到既culture shock。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n商場地底有個平民d既美食廣場，見到好多人去搵食。<br />\n<img src=\"https://travellingangel.files.wordpress.com/2011/01/842359_f520.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftravellingangel.files.wordpress.com%2F2011%2F01%2F842359_f520.jpg&h=81bad08a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n空位唔多，我買完碟飯咁岩見到有張空枱就狗衝過去。<br />\n枱上面有２包紙巾，呢一點新加坡人做得好體貼，連food court都提供紙巾畀食客使用，夠哂衛生。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n再望下周圍，幾乎每張空枱上面都有d紙巾。<br />\nd人話新加坡人非常注重乾淨，真係一d都冇錯。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n食食下有個大媽走埋黎，指住包紙巾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：這位置是我先佔的。<br />\n我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：哦？SORRY <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我唔介意同人搭枱，只係估唔到包紙巾係用拎霸位，大鄉里出城既我覺得好撚離譜。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大媽拎走紙巾環顧四周，走左去隔離張枱坐。<br />\n<br />\n其實新加坡人都唔係想像中咁有文化。<br />\n後來上網search下，先發現呢個係新加坡獨有既food court霸位文化。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/ycb2fjep\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fycb2fjep&h=85c02193&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/SimonShenGlobalMicrocosm/posts/1960481590897228\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FSimonShenGlobalMicrocosm%2Fposts%2F1960481590897228&d=dG8WLkYDNMcC3X2tWQInyAKEmdudW1rq3V1Y15kzxIU%3D&h=8ae567f4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/SimonShenGlobalMicrocosm/posts/1960481590897228</a><br />\n以後去新加坡，可以試下入鄉隨俗帶紙巾霸枱。"},{"pid":"7b346e4d2e19303f91ede336aa7c761111df9d17","tid":328497,"uid":1567,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T04:36:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>空位唔多，我買完碟飯咁岩見到有張空枱就狗衝過去。<br />\n枱上面有２包紙巾，呢一點新加坡人做得好體貼，連food court都提供紙巾畀食客使用，夠哂衛生。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n再望下周圍，幾乎每張空枱上面都有d紙巾。<br />\nd人話新加坡人非常注重乾淨，真係食食下有個大媽走埋黎，指住包紙巾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：這位置是我先佔的。<br />\n我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：哦？SORRY <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我唔介意同人搭枱，只係估唔到包紙巾係用拎霸位，大鄉里出城既我覺得好撚離譜。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大媽拎走紙巾環顧四周，走左去隔離張枱坐。</blockquote><br />\n見你係遊客已經算客氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n正常應該會鬧你you blind ah? tissue here cannot see meh? this table i chope already!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c5439cdff2084c1b047858525f7d12658eedfc0","tid":328497,"uid":1567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T04:41:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/iLPkF33l46A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FiLPkF33l46A&d=dG8WLkYDNMcC3X2tWQInyAKEmdudW1rq3V1Y15kzxIU%3D&h=6fa9475e\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/iLPkF